<hw>Midst</hw>, <pos>prep.</pos> <def>In the midst of; amidst.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Midst</ent>⟦br⟧

